    public static interface SoyFileSupplier.Version
    An opaque identifier that can be compared for equality with other versions from the same resource.

    Instances are not Comparable since a version is not necessarily monotonic ; e.g. a cryptographically strong hash function produces a more reliable version identifier than a time-stamp but not one that can be said to be newer or older than any other version.
